SELECT MIN(T1.image_id), T2.section_title FROM Images AS T1 JOIN Document_Sections_Images AS T3 ON T3.image_id = T1.image_id JOIN Document_Sections AS T2 ON T2.section_id = T3.section_id JOIN Documents AS T4 ON T4.document_code = T2.document_code WHERE T2.section_id = 97

SELECT DISTINCT T1.section_title FROM Document_Sections AS T1 INNER JOIN Document_Sections_Images AS T2 ON T1.section_id = T2.section_id INNER JOIN Images AS T3 ON T2.image_id = T3.image_id WHERE T1.section_sequence > 77 AND T1.document_code IN (SELECT document_code FROM Documents WHERE access_count BETWEEN 1 AND 10)
SELECT section_sequence, section_id FROM Document_Sections WHERE section_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  section_sequence = 54 ORDER BY section_sequence DESC LIMIT 8
SELECT Documents.document_structure_code FROM Documents JOIN Document_Structures ON Documents.document_structure_code = Document_Structures.document_structure_code WHERE access_count BETWEEN 1 AND 10
SELECT COUNT(m.section_id), m.section_id FROM Document_Sections AS m WHERE m.section_sequence BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  m.section_id >= 33 ORDER BY m.section_id LIMIT 9;
SELECT AVG(b.section_id), MIN(b.section_sequence) FROM Document_Sections AS b WHERE  b.section_sequence > 84

SELECT MAX(access_count), access_count FROM Documents JOIN Document_Structures ON Documents.document_structure_code = Document_Structures.document_structure_code WHERE access_count > 97 ORDER BY access_count ASC
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT s.user_id), s.password FROM Users AS s WHERE  s.user_id > 100
SELECT t.functional_area_code FROM Document_Functional_Areas AS t ORDER BY t.functional_area_code ASC
SELECT user_id FROM Users WHERE user_id != 97;
SELECT image_name, AVG(image_id) FROM Images WHERE image_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY image_name;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT image_name) FROM Images WHERE image_id != 1;

SELECT T3.access_count, T2.section_code FROM Document_Sections AS T1 JOIN Document_Sections AS T2 ON T1.section_id = T2.section_id JOIN Documents AS T3 ON T2.document_code = T3.document_code JOIN Document_Functional_Areas AS T4 ON T1.section_id = T4.section_id WHERE T3.access_count > 35 ORDER BY T3.access_count ASC
SELECT section_id FROM Documents JOIN Document_Sections ON Document_Sections.document_code = Documents.document_code WHERE  section_sequence < 90 ORDER BY section_id ASC

SELECT MIN(T3.image_id), T2.section_sequence FROM Documents AS T1 JOIN Document_Sections AS T2 ON T1.document_code = T2.document_code JOIN Document_Sections_Images AS T3 ON T2.section_id = T3.section_id WHERE T1.access_count < 19
SELECT MIN(access_count) FROM Documents WHERE  access_count != 22 LIMIT 9
SELECT T1.image_alt_text FROM Document_Sections_Images AS T2 JOIN Images AS T1 ON T2.image_id = T1.image_id WHERE T2.image_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND T2.section_id != 51
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT j.user_id), j.user_id, j.user_name FROM Users AS j WHERE j.user_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY j.user_id, j.user_name LIMIT 4
SELECT MIN(x.user_id) AS min_user_id, COUNT(x.user_id) AS user_count, x.password FROM Users AS x WHERE  x.user_id <= 14 GROUP BY x.password HAVING SUM(x.user_id) = 95 ORDER BY x.password DESC

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT section_sequence) FROM Document_Sections JOIN Document_Sections_Images ON Document_Sections.section_id = Document_Sections_Images.section_id WHERE  Document_Sections.section_id <= 6
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT section_sequence) FROM Document_Sections WHERE section_id != 2

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT document_code), section_sequence FROM Document_Sections JOIN Document_Sections_Images ON Document_Sections.section_id = Document_Sections_Images.section_id WHERE Document_Sections_Images.section_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10 OR  image_id <= 15

SELECT password, user_login FROM Roles JOIN Users ON Users.role_code = Roles.role_code WHERE role_code IN (SELECT role_code FROM Users AS c WHERE c.user_id BETWEEN 1 AND 10) GROUP BY user_login HAVING MIN(user_id) = 54
